strings.Value: "What lies ahead?"
"Do you know where the kobold shaman Tartuk is now?"
"How do I get to this broken passage?"
[Attack] "I am your ally no longer."
"Here are the mandibles you asked for."
"I must go. Farewell!"
"That's why they're called centipedes â€” because of the scent!"
"When I become a baron{mf||ess}, I'm instituting a law against puns..."
[Say nothing]

"Daisy, come! Good girl!"
{n}The gatekeeper notices you and her face lights up. She turns away from her pet centipede.{/n} "Greeting, ally! You come. Warrior Queen Bdaah wait you." {n}The gatekeeper sighs in delight.{/n} "Queen beauty as little centipede!"

"Hole under Old Sycamore, here live mite and our animal. Careful, some animal still wild! There deep hole, very dangerous! Up was kobold passage, but now it broken. Kobold drop stones, we lift bridge. No passage. Sad! Rich chest lie passage. Big treasure. All lost now."
"Shaman Purple Hide? Know not! He run our hole, throw magic. Queen chase him. Queen know where he."

"Lower bridge bad! Kobold run away on bridge." {n}The gatekeeper thinks for a while.{/n} "Ally make trade, yes? You want passage. I want pretty helmet. You go lower passage deep, there lie big dead spider. Our great warrior hero mount it, until die. Bring me this bug jaw, I give you lever for bridge. You take chest with loot, I make helmet of spider. Sweet!"
"All good! I make fine helmet. Take lever bridge, brave ally. I say no one, you take treasure."
"Need more kobold. Daisy eat them fast, then hungry... Greeting, ally!"
"Would that I could banish the word 'beauty' from the maws of these filthy creatures."
"These things are creepy! I almost... centi-peed my pants! Ha ha ha!"
{n}Regongar laughs.{/n}
"Then I'll just go underground and start a guerilla war, ha ha!"
{n}Realizing his joke is going unnoticed, Regongar frowns and grunts.{/n}
